WEBVTT

00:02.029 --> 00:04.025
SPICE...

00:04.027 --> 00:06.022
AND EVERYTHING NICE.

00:06.024 --> 00:08.003
THESE WERE
THE INGREDIENTS CHOSEN

00:08.005 --> 00:10.020
TO CREATE THE PERFECT
LITTLE GIRL.

00:10.022 --> 00:12.021
BUT PROFESSOR UTONIUM
ACCIDENTALLY ADDED

00:12.023 --> 00:15.015
AN EXTRA INGREDIENT
TO THE CONCOCTION--

00:15.017 --> 00:16.019
CHEMICAL X.

00:16.021 --> 00:18.009
[EXPLOSION]

00:20.005 --> 00:22.021
THUS THE POWERPUFF GIRLS
WERE BORN!

00:22.023 --> 00:24.017
USING
THEIR ULTRA-SUPERPOWERS,

00:24.019 --> 00:27.000
BLOSSOM, BUBBLES,
AND BUTTERCUP

00:27.002 --> 00:28.012
HAVE DEDICATED
THEIR LIVES

00:28.014 --> 00:31.029
TO FIGHTING CRIME
AND THE FORCES OF EVIL!

01:00.027 --> 01:03.017
CAPTIONING MADE POSSIBLE BY
TURNER ENTERTAINMENT GROUP
AND U.S. DEPARTMENT OF EDUCATION

01:16.002 --> 01:18.000
Narrator: THE CITY
OF TOWNSVILLE...

01:18.002 --> 01:19.009
IS UNDER ATTACK!

01:19.011 --> 01:21.012
[ROARING]

01:25.010 --> 01:27.001
THE POWERPUFF GIRLS!

01:41.028 --> 01:43.023
WHEE!

01:43.025 --> 01:45.028
WHEE!

01:46.000 --> 01:47.004
WHEE!

01:47.006 --> 01:51.002
Narrator: IT SEEMS ONCE AGAIN,
THE DAY IS SAVED.

01:51.004 --> 01:52.011
WHEE! WHEE!

01:52.013 --> 01:53.018
BUT WHAT'S THIS?

01:53.020 --> 01:55.029
IT APPEARS OUR GIRLS
ARE SECRETLY BEING MONITORED,

01:56.001 --> 01:58.007
BUT BY WHOM?
OH, NO! NOT--

01:58.009 --> 02:00.017
I--I--I CAN'T SAY IT!

02:00.019 --> 02:03.007
THIS IS A VILLAIN
SO EVIL, SO SINISTER,

02:03.009 --> 02:06.016
SO HORRIBLY VILE THAT
EVEN THE UTTERANCE OF HIS NAME

02:06.018 --> 02:09.007
STRIKES FEAR
INTO THE HEARTS OF MEN!

02:09.009 --> 02:12.010
THE ONLY SAFE WAY TO REFER
TO THIS KING OF DARKNESS

02:12.012 --> 02:14.016
IS SIMPLY...

02:14.018 --> 02:15.011
HIM.

02:16.029 --> 02:21.013
OH, SNAKE BEAST,

02:21.015 --> 02:25.008
YOU DIDN'T
DESTROY THEM
AT ALL, DID YOU?

02:25.010 --> 02:29.003
HOW COULD
YOU LET THE
POWERPUFF GIRLS

02:29.005 --> 02:35.011
HUMILIATE YOU
SO COMPLETELY,
HMM?

02:35.013 --> 02:37.001
YO, BLOSSOM!
CATCH!

02:38.018 --> 02:42.000
BUTTERCUP,
NOT SO HARD! AAH!

02:44.012 --> 02:46.028
WELL, MISS BELLUM,
YOU CAN GET BACK
TO WORK NOW.

02:49.012 --> 02:50.022
SORRY ABOUT THAT,
MAYOR.

02:50.024 --> 02:52.010
OH, THAT'S OK.

02:52.012 --> 02:55.005
IT WOULDN'T HAVE HAPPENED
IF BUTTERCUP WOULDN'T
THROW SO HARD.

02:55.007 --> 02:57.002
IF YOU COULD
ONLY CATCH--

02:57.004 --> 02:58.007
YOU THREW IT TOO HARD.

02:58.009 --> 02:59.014
DID NOT!
DID TOO!

02:59.016 --> 03:00.023
DID NOT!
DID TOO!

03:00.025 --> 03:02.002
STOP IT!

03:02.004 --> 03:05.004
I HATE IT
WHEN YOU GUYS FIGHT.

03:05.006 --> 03:07.012
[REWINDING]

03:07.014 --> 03:09.019
...HATE IT
WHEN YOU GUYS FIGHT.

03:09.021 --> 03:10.029
[REWINDING]

03:11.001 --> 03:13.010
...WHEN YOU GUYS FIGHT.

03:13.012 --> 03:17.007
YES! YES!

03:17.009 --> 03:19.014
WELL, I LOVE IT
WHEN YOU GIRLS FIGHT.

03:19.016 --> 03:23.002
I THINK YOU SHOULD FIGHT
MORE OFTEN. HA HA!

03:23.004 --> 03:25.019
OH, BUBBLES...

03:25.021 --> 03:28.007
DON'T CRY, LITTLE ONE.

03:28.009 --> 03:33.007
I'M HERE FOR YOU. HA HA!

03:34.008 --> 03:35.016
Narrator:
SO AFTER SAVING THE DAY,

03:35.018 --> 03:39.000
THE GIRLS RETURN HOME
FOR SOME PEACE AND QUIET.

03:39.002 --> 03:40.027
Blossom:
SHUT UP, BUTTERCUP!

03:40.029 --> 03:42.006
WELL, MAYBE NOT.

03:42.008 --> 03:43.008
NO! YOU SHUT UP!

03:43.010 --> 03:44.025
YOU SHUT UP!

03:44.027 --> 03:48.006
GIRLS!
UM, STOP THAT--

03:48.008 --> 03:50.006
GIRLS, YOU'RE--
STOP THAT ARGUING.

03:50.008 --> 03:50.025
SHUT UP!

03:50.027 --> 03:52.008
YOU SHUT UP!

03:52.010 --> 03:53.005
SHUT UP!

03:53.007 --> 03:55.017
SHUT UP!

03:55.019 --> 03:59.007
[SOBBING]

04:02.003 --> 04:05.001
OH, I DON'T LIKE
ARGUING.

04:05.003 --> 04:08.018
WHY CAN'T WE ALL
JUST GET ALONG,

04:08.020 --> 04:11.021
INSTEAD
OF FIGHTING AND ARGUING?

04:11.023 --> 04:13.004
[CRYING]

04:14.012 --> 04:16.002
Him, whispering:
Bubbles...

04:16.004 --> 04:18.019
Bubbles...

04:18.021 --> 04:21.019
HUH? WHO SAID THAT?

04:21.021 --> 04:23.002
Bubbles...

04:23.004 --> 04:24.025
[GASP]

04:24.027 --> 04:26.023
OCTI?

04:33.014 --> 04:37.015
YES, BUBBLES.
I CAN TALK,

04:37.017 --> 04:42.005
AND I HEARD WHAT
YOU WERE SAYING
ABOUT YOUR SISTERS.

04:42.007 --> 04:44.015
YOU'RE RIGHT,
BUBBLES.

04:44.017 --> 04:47.004
IT'S WRONG
FOR THEM TO FIGHT.

04:47.006 --> 04:48.029
YOU <i>ARE</i><i>TALKING.</i>

04:49.001 --> 04:50.018
YES, BUBBLES.

04:50.020 --> 04:55.002
COME CLOSER SO I CAN
TELL YOU MORE.

04:55.004 --> 04:56.011
Buttercup:
DON'T TELL ME
WHAT TO DO!

04:56.013 --> 04:58.001
Blossom: JUST LISTEN
TO ME NEXT TIME!

04:58.003 --> 05:00.028
LET'S NOT LISTEN
TO THAT ANYMORE.

05:01.001 --> 05:03.012
LISTEN,
IN MY OPINION,

05:03.014 --> 05:07.011
BLOSSOM IS BEING
FAR TOO BOSSY
FOR HER OWN GOOD.

05:07.013 --> 05:10.019
IN FACT, I THINK
THAT BUTTERCUP

05:10.021 --> 05:12.005
SHOULD BE IN CHARGE.

05:12.007 --> 05:14.028
YEAH. THAT'S IT.

05:15.000 --> 05:17.024
BUBBLES, YOU SHOULD
TALK TO BUTTERCUP

05:17.026 --> 05:21.026
AND TELL HER
THAT SHE SHOULD BE
RUNNING THE SHOW.

05:21.028 --> 05:25.029
Narrator: OH, WHAT DID
I TELL YOU ABOUT HIM?

05:26.001 --> 05:28.028
EVIL.
EVIL, PURE AND SIMPLE!

05:31.009 --> 05:33.012
[BUZZ BUZZ BUZZ]

05:33.014 --> 05:36.019
YES, MAYOR? WHAT?
WE'LL BE RIGHT THERE!

05:38.015 --> 05:40.011
[ROARING]

05:40.013 --> 05:41.009
EVERYBODY READY?

05:41.011 --> 05:41.028
READY!

05:43.008 --> 05:46.004
BUBBLES,
PUT DOWN THAT DOLL!
YOU KNOW BETTER!

05:48.029 --> 05:51.022
OCTI, I HAVE TO
PUT YOU DOWN.

05:51.024 --> 05:55.024
WHY? JUST BECAUSE
BLOSSOM TOLD YOU TO?

05:55.026 --> 05:59.012
BUT--
BLOSSOM'S NOT ALWAYS
RIGHT, YOU KNOW.

05:59.014 --> 06:00.014
OH?

06:00.016 --> 06:02.012
GO FOR THE HEAD!

06:06.015 --> 06:07.007
[GASP]

06:07.009 --> 06:08.028
BLOSSOM!
BUTTERCUP!

06:09.000 --> 06:11.014
YOU SEE?

06:11.016 --> 06:13.000
HEY,
LET'S TRY MY--

06:13.002 --> 06:14.019
GO FOR THE ARMS!

06:14.021 --> 06:16.010
YOUR PLANS
AREN'T WORKING!

06:16.012 --> 06:17.020
UH, BUTTERCUP?

06:17.022 --> 06:18.019
WHAT, BUBBLES?

06:18.021 --> 06:20.013
UM, WELL, UH...

06:20.015 --> 06:22.029
OCTI SAYS YOU SHOULD DO
WHAT <i>YOU</i><i>WANT TO DO.</i>

06:23.001 --> 06:24.017
DON'T FOLLOW BLOSSOM.

06:24.019 --> 06:27.018
OCTI,
YOU'RE SPEAKING
MY LANGUAGE.

06:28.022 --> 06:31.016
BUTTERCUP,
WHERE ARE YOU? WHOA!

06:33.017 --> 06:34.027
[GRUNTING]

06:40.025 --> 06:42.013
BUTTERCUP, DON'T!

06:47.019 --> 06:48.025
OH, NO!

06:48.027 --> 06:51.017
Narrator: IT'S HEADED
RIGHT FOR THAT SENIOR CITIZEN!

06:55.011 --> 06:56.008
OH, NO!

06:56.010 --> 06:57.020
[CRASH]

07:02.022 --> 07:03.024
OOPS.

07:10.006 --> 07:12.002
YOU RECKLESSLY
ENDANGERED
PEOPLE'S LIVES!

07:12.004 --> 07:14.001
DID NOT!
AND FAILED
TO FOLLOW ORDERS!

07:14.003 --> 07:16.017
I SHOULD BE THE
LEADER ANYWAY!

07:16.019 --> 07:18.002
GIRLS, CALM DOWN!

07:18.004 --> 07:19.006
NO!                 NO!

07:19.008 --> 07:21.002
I'VE HAD IT WITH
YOUR INSUBORDINATION!

07:25.017 --> 07:27.024
WELL, I'VE
HAD IT WITH
YOUR LEADERSHIP!

07:32.017 --> 07:35.005
WELL, I SUPPOSE
IT WAS INEVITABLE.

07:35.007 --> 07:38.011
I ALWAYS KNEW
THEY WOULDN'T LAST

07:38.013 --> 07:41.021
ON THE SAME TEAM!
HA HA HA!

07:41.023 --> 07:44.011
WITH BLOSSOM
AND BUTTERCUP
BUSY FIGHTING,

07:44.013 --> 07:48.016
BUBBLES DOESN'T
STAND A CHANCE!
HEE HEE HEE!

07:48.018 --> 07:53.011
MORE, MORE, MORE,
MORE, MORE, MORE!

07:53.013 --> 07:55.001
I'VE ALWAYS BEEN
THE LEADER!

07:55.003 --> 07:59.008
THAT'S ENOUGH! I'VE GOT
TO SEPARATE YOU TWO!
GO HAVE A TIME-OUT!

07:59.010 --> 08:00.019
OH, OCTI...

08:00.021 --> 08:02.022
NOW THEY'RE
FIGHTING MORE
THAN EVER.

08:02.024 --> 08:05.022
I'M SO CONFUSED.

08:05.024 --> 08:09.016
OCTI, TELL ME
WHAT TO DO.

08:10.015 --> 08:13.000
OCTI?
WHY DON'T YOU
SAY SOMETHING?

08:14.020 --> 08:17.025
STUPID LITTLE GIRL.

08:17.027 --> 08:18.029
HUH?

08:23.024 --> 08:25.028
THEY'RE FIGHTING
BECAUSE OF YOU,

08:26.000 --> 08:29.009
BECAUSE YOU BELIEVE
YOUR TOYS CAN
REALLY TALK

08:29.011 --> 08:33.006
AND YOU ACTUALLY
DO WHAT THEY
TELL YOU TO DO.

08:33.008 --> 08:36.006
I KNOW THAT VOICE.
YOU'RE...

08:36.008 --> 08:37.008
HIM!

08:37.010 --> 08:39.002
VERY GOOD!
I'M FLATTERED.

08:39.004 --> 08:40.029
BUT THANK YOU,
BUBBLES.

08:41.001 --> 08:42.019
THANK YOU
FOR HELPING ME
BREAK UP

08:42.021 --> 08:45.026
THE POWERPUFF
GIRLS ONCE
AND FOR ALL.

08:45.028 --> 08:49.022
NOW, IF YOU'LL
EXCUSE ME,
I MUST GO...

08:49.024 --> 08:52.018
AND DESTROY
THE WORLD!

08:55.009 --> 08:57.029
OH, NO! HE'S HEADED
STRAIGHT FOR TOWNSVILLE!

08:58.001 --> 09:02.012
I'VE GOT TO STOP HIM
MYSELF. I JUST HOPE
I DON'T MESS THIS UP, TOO.

09:07.015 --> 09:11.011
[PEOPLE SCREAMING]

09:11.013 --> 09:13.002
[TIRES SCREECHING]

09:27.023 --> 09:30.019
STOP! YOU USED ME!

09:30.021 --> 09:34.008
OH, IS THAT
WHAT I DID?

09:34.010 --> 09:36.002
THAT'S NOT FAIR!

09:36.004 --> 09:39.027
NO, IT ISN'T.
NEITHER IS THIS!

09:39.029 --> 09:41.027
AAH!

09:43.004 --> 09:45.003
Both: BUBBLES
IS IN TROUBLE!

10:06.019 --> 10:08.025
AAH!

10:20.006 --> 10:22.025
WHAT?! BLOSSOM
AND BUTTERCUP?!

10:22.027 --> 10:25.014
BUT YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO BE FIGHTING
EACH OTHER!

10:25.016 --> 10:27.000
SOME THINGS
ARE JUST
MORE IMPORTANT.

10:27.002 --> 10:28.016
RIGHT,
BUTTERCUP?
RIGHT!

10:28.018 --> 10:30.019
HA HA HA!

10:30.021 --> 10:34.008
NO! NO! NO!

10:39.014 --> 10:41.020
NO...

10:43.017 --> 10:45.021
Buttercup: WHEW!
I'M GLAD THAT'S OVER.

10:45.023 --> 10:48.024
UH, HEY, BLOSSOM?
I'M SORRY ABOUT
FIGHTING WITH YOU.

10:48.026 --> 10:50.027
ME, TOO. YOU KNOW,
WE'RE LUCKY

10:50.029 --> 10:52.011
TO HAVE A SISTER
LIKE BUBBLES,

10:52.013 --> 10:54.024
WHO WAS ONLY
TRYING TO REMIND US
THAT WE'RE A TEAM.

10:54.026 --> 10:57.009
YEAH, AND THAT ANY PERSONAL
DIFFERENCES WE'VE GOT

10:57.011 --> 10:59.021
SHOULDN'T STOP US FROM
SAVING THE DAY AND STUFF.

10:59.023 --> 11:02.026
HA HA HA!
FOR ALL MY HARD WORK,

11:02.028 --> 11:05.027
I SHOULD BE
THE LEADER!

11:05.029 --> 11:07.027
HA HA HA!
HA HA HA!
HA HA HA!

11:08.000 --> 11:09.008
Narrator: HA HA HA!
YOU TELL 'EM, BUBBLES.

11:09.010 --> 11:12.024
SO ONCE AGAIN,
THE DAY IS SAVED,

11:12.026 --> 11:15.015
THANKS
TO THE POWERPUFF GIRLS!

11:32.005 --> 11:35.013
Narrator:
THE CITY OF TOWNSVILLE,
A PLACE FILLED WITH SOME

11:35.015 --> 11:38.006
OF THE MOST BRILLIANT,
CLEVER, AND INGENIOUS
CRIMINAL MASTERMINDS

11:38.008 --> 11:39.028
EVER TO HATCH
AN EVIL SCHEME.

11:40.000 --> 11:42.016
THEN THERE'S
THE AMEBA BOYS.

11:52.004 --> 11:54.019
HEH HEH HEH!
WE DID IT!

11:54.021 --> 11:57.009
WE'RE OFFICIAL
CRIMINALS.

11:57.011 --> 11:58.012
YEAH, CRIMINALS.

11:58.014 --> 12:00.018
HEE HEE! YEAH.

12:00.020 --> 12:02.015
SO COME ON.
LET'S SEE IT.

12:02.017 --> 12:03.023
YEAH,
LET'S SEE IT.

12:03.025 --> 12:05.001
DUH, SEE IT?

12:05.003 --> 12:06.002
YEAH.
THE ORANGE.

12:06.004 --> 12:07.016
LET'S SEE
THE ORANGE.

12:07.018 --> 12:09.001
YEAH, THE ORANGE.

12:09.003 --> 12:10.017
OH, THAT.

12:10.019 --> 12:12.010
YES, THAT.
THE ORANGE,

12:12.012 --> 12:14.020
THE FRUIT
THAT YOU STOLE
JUST NOW.

12:14.022 --> 12:16.011
LET'S SEE IT!

12:16.013 --> 12:17.019
[NERVOUS LAUGH]

12:17.021 --> 12:19.029
WHAT DO YOU WANT
TO SEE THAT FOR?

12:20.001 --> 12:22.003
PRODUCE THE PRODUCE.

12:22.005 --> 12:24.022
YOU DIDN'T TAKE IT,
DID YOU?

12:24.024 --> 12:26.007
HE DIDN'T TAKE IT,
BOSS.

12:26.009 --> 12:30.010
I WAS GOING TO,
BUT THAT WOULD
BE STEALING.

12:30.012 --> 12:32.012
AAH! THAT'S IT!

12:32.014 --> 12:35.013
I SPENT MONTHS PLANNING
THAT ORANGE HEIST,

12:35.015 --> 12:37.008
AND YOU GO AND CHOKE
AT THE LAST MINUTE.

12:37.010 --> 12:39.014
DON'T YOU HAVE
ANY BACKBONE, YOU--

12:39.016 --> 12:40.022
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

12:40.024 --> 12:44.005
LISTEN. OOH, THAT CAN
ONLY MEAN ONE THING.

12:46.021 --> 12:50.002
NOW'S OUR CHANCE
TO GET IN <i>REAL</i><i>TROUBLE.</i>

12:50.004 --> 12:53.014
HEY, POWERPUFF GIRLS!

12:55.014 --> 12:56.014
WHAT?

12:56.016 --> 12:59.018
UH...UH...UH...

12:59.020 --> 13:01.028
AHA!
CHECK IT OUT!

13:10.029 --> 13:12.023
LITTERING.

13:12.025 --> 13:14.017
SORRY, GUYS.
YOU'RE GOING
TO HAVE TO

13:14.019 --> 13:15.020
DO BETTER
THAN THAT.

13:15.022 --> 13:17.003
COME ON, GIRLS.
LET'S GO.

13:17.005 --> 13:20.003
NO! WAIT! SO YOU WANT
TO SEE A CRIME, HUH?

13:20.005 --> 13:22.023
HUH?
A REAL CRIME?

13:22.025 --> 13:24.009
YEAH. SURE. OK.

13:24.011 --> 13:25.012
Bubbles:
SOUNDS FUN.

13:25.014 --> 13:26.023
Buttercup:
OH, BROTHER.

13:26.025 --> 13:28.010
COME ON, THEN!

13:28.012 --> 13:29.019
Narrator:
TOWNSVILLE PARK--

13:29.021 --> 13:32.028
A CLEAN PLACE FOR CLEAN FOLKS
TO HAVE GOOD CLEAN FUN.

13:40.028 --> 13:42.008
LITTERING.

13:42.010 --> 13:45.007
OH, BROTHER.
LOOK, GUYS,
WE'VE GOT TO GO.

13:45.009 --> 13:46.026
NO! WAIT!

13:46.028 --> 13:49.008
COME BACK! DON'T GO!

13:49.010 --> 13:51.020
YEAH, DON'T GO!

13:56.014 --> 13:58.018
DON'T MOVE, YOU MUGS.
THIS COULD BE IT--

13:58.020 --> 14:01.009
THE CRIME
OF THE CENTURY!

14:16.012 --> 14:19.027
[ALL SNORING]

14:24.022 --> 14:26.005
AH-CHOO!

14:26.007 --> 14:27.022
ARE WE IN JAIL YET?

14:27.024 --> 14:29.020
SHUT UP, STUPID.

14:29.022 --> 14:32.009
YEAH, SHUT UP.

14:32.011 --> 14:34.009
[COUGHING]

14:34.011 --> 14:38.009
HEY, BOSS,
I DON'T FEEL SO GOOD.

14:38.011 --> 14:41.023
AH-AH-AH-CHOO!

14:41.025 --> 14:42.028
AH-CHOO!

14:43.000 --> 14:44.002
GESUNDHEIT.

14:44.004 --> 14:45.028
YEAH,
GESUNDHEIT.

14:49.028 --> 14:51.028
AH-AH-AH-CHOO!

14:59.008 --> 15:02.009
AH-AH-AH-AH-CHOO!

15:07.013 --> 15:10.027
[ALL SNEEZING
AND COUGHING]

15:19.011 --> 15:20.023
[TELEPHONES RINGING]

15:20.025 --> 15:22.005
HELLO? WHAT?

15:22.007 --> 15:24.017
YOU CAN'T COME IN?
YOU'RE SICK? WHAT?

15:24.019 --> 15:27.002
HELLO? YOU'RE SICK, TOO?
YOU CAN'T COME IN?

15:27.004 --> 15:29.003
HELLO? HELLO?
YOU'RE SICK?

15:29.005 --> 15:31.010
SICK! SICK!
EVERYONE'S SICK!

15:31.012 --> 15:32.024
OH, MISS BELLUM,

15:32.026 --> 15:34.014
THANK GOODNESS
YOU'RE HERE.

15:34.016 --> 15:36.017
THE WHOLE TOWN IS SICK.
YOU'VE GOT TO DO SOME--

15:36.019 --> 15:38.016
AH-AH-CHOO!

15:38.018 --> 15:39.025
OH, NO.

15:39.027 --> 15:42.008
AH-AH-AH-CHOO!

15:42.010 --> 15:44.011
OH, NOW I'VE GOT IT, TOO.

15:44.013 --> 15:46.018
THERE'S ONLY
ONE THING TO DO.

15:48.021 --> 15:50.001
[BUZZING]

15:50.003 --> 15:52.015
I'LL GET IT!

15:52.017 --> 15:54.022
YES, MAYOR?
WHAT'S THE TROUBLE?

15:54.024 --> 15:56.022
HUH?
YOU'RE SICK?

15:56.024 --> 16:00.029
WELL, THAT'S TOO BAD,
MR. MAYOR, BUT IT DOESN'T
SOUND LIKE AN EMERGENCY.

16:01.001 --> 16:03.011
NOW, TELL EVERYONE
TO GET LOTS OF REST

16:03.013 --> 16:05.000
AND DRINK
PLENTY OF LIQUIDS.

16:05.002 --> 16:08.008
AND ONLY CALL
WHEN THERE'S A <i>REAL</i><i>EMERGENCY.</i>

16:08.010 --> 16:11.027
REMEMBER, THE HOTLINE
IS NOT A TOY.

16:13.014 --> 16:16.006
[MUSIC PLAYING]

16:17.020 --> 16:19.012
ICE CREAM!
ICE CREAM!

16:19.014 --> 16:22.004
[CHEERING]

16:22.006 --> 16:23.029
AH-AH-CHOO!

16:27.004 --> 16:29.019
UNH! AH-CHOO!

16:29.021 --> 16:31.013
EW!
EW!
EW!

16:31.015 --> 16:34.013
MAYBE THE MAYOR
WASN'T KIDDING.
LET'S GO!

16:35.008 --> 16:37.016
[CHEERING]

16:40.002 --> 16:41.003
UH-OH. LOOK!

16:41.005 --> 16:43.007
Bubbles:
EVERYBODY'S
SLEEPING.

16:43.009 --> 16:47.005
Blossom: NO, BUBBLES.
THERE'S BEEN AN OUTBREAK
OF SOME TERRIBLE DISEASE!

16:50.026 --> 16:54.002
WE'VE GOT TO HELP
THESE PEOPLE!
LET'S MOVE!

16:54.020 --> 16:56.003
HEY, BLOSSOM...

16:56.005 --> 16:57.016
[COUGH COUGH COUGH]

